Goals:
-Application to allow users to maintain their inventory by keeping track of inventory levels
-Application to allow users to track their profit margins by producing a monthly and yearly report based on past, current, and marketing data

Objectives:
-	To maintain inventory by having a baseline stored-inventory-threshold that user can set and tracking number of items sold and added to inventory.
-	To control the inventory size by updating the total inventory every time an item is sold or added.
-	To organize the inventory by allowing user to group and search an item alphabetically or based on category of genre, author, keyword, and ISBN.
-Application sends a profit margin report to user using information attained from inventory category, popularity, cost, and title of items sold versus unsold

